
---

## `.gitignore` for deployment

**Deploy version** ka matlab: aisi `.gitignore` jo Render deploy ko break na kare.  
Isliye **ML model files ignore nahi karenge**.

```gitignore
# =========================
# Node
# =========================
**/node_modules/

# =========================
# Python
# =========================
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd

# =========================
# Environment files
# =========================
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# =========================
# Logs
# =========================
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# =========================
# Build output
# =========================
**/dist/
**/build/

# =========================
# IDE / OS files
# =========================
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# =========================
# Misc
# =========================
*.swp
*.swo